data.title: About IBM Knowledge Center for Rational Software Architect
data.meta_description: The IBM Knowledge Center provides you with user assistance for each version of IBM Rational Software Architect, Rational Software Architect for WebSphere, Rational Software Architect RealTime Edition,  Rational Software Architect Standard Edition and Rational Software Architect Design Manager.  With IBM Knowledge Center, you can view, browse, and search online information related to the Rational Software Architect family.
data.text:
Content

IBM Knowledge Center provides a powerful on-line interface for finding technical information on a particular product, offering, or product solution.

IBM Knowledge Center is designed to:

Help you plan, install, configure, use, tune, monitor, troubleshoot, and maintain the product

Contain reference material such as product commands, parameters, and system values

IMPORTANT: Language of the content displayed in IBM Knowledge Center is determined by the Language setting in your browser, if the content is available in that language.

From IBM Knowledge Center, all the major documentation can be accessed.

Click and scroll to find the IBM Knowledge Center for your product.

Rational Software Architect

Rational Software Architect for 7.x, 8.x and 9.x and beyond in the IBM Knowledge Center and Rational Software Architect Design Manager 5.0.x (which is in the same IBM Knowledge Center collection as Rational Software Architect 9.1.0).

Rational Software Architect Design Manager

Rational Software Architect Design Manager for 3.0.x and 4.0.x in the IBM Knowledge Center.

Rational Software Architect RealTime Edition

Rational Software Architect RealTime Edition for 7.5.x, 8.0.x, 8.5.x and 9.x and beyond in the IBM Knowledge Center.

Rational Software Architect for WebSphere Software

Rational Software Architect for WebSphere Software for 7.x, 8.x and 9.x and beyond in the IBM Knowledge Center.
